quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  23,51,"ya 'ayuha alrusul kuluu min tayib alrizq alhlal, waemaluu al'aemal alsalht, 'iiniy bima taemalun elym, la yakhfaa ely shay' min aemalkm. walkhitab fi alayat eam llrsl- ealayhim alslam- watbaehm, wafi alayat dalil ealaa 'ana 'akl alhlal eawn ealaa aleamal alsalh, wa'ana eaqibat alharam wkhymt, waminha rada aldea'"
  23,52,"w'inn dynkm- ya maeshar alanbya'- din wahid wahu al'islam, wa'ana rabukum fatqwny bamtthal awamry wajtnab zwajry"
  23,53,"ftfrraq alatbae fi aldiyn 'iilaa 'ahzab wshye, jaealuu dinahum adyanana baedama 'umru balajtmae, kl hizb mejb brayh zaem 'anah ealaa alhaqi wghyrh ealaa albatl. wafi hdha tahdhir min althzb waltfrq fi aldyn"
  23,54,fatrkhm - 'ayuha alrasul - fi dalalatihim wjhlhm bialhaqi 'iilaa 'an yunazil aleadhab bhm
  23,55,"ayzn hwla' alkufaar 'ana ma nmdduhm bih min 'amwal wawlad fi aldunya hu tejyl khyr lahum ysthqwnh? 'iinama nejl lahum alkhayr fitnatan lahum wastdrajana, wlknhm la yuhissun bdhlk"
  23,56,"ayzn hwla' alkufaar 'ana ma nmdduhm bih min 'amwal wawlad fi aldunya hu tejyl khyr lahum ysthqwnh? 'iinama nejl lahum alkhayr fitnatan lahum wastdrajana, wlknhm la yuhissun bdhlk"
  23,57,'inn aladhin hum min khashyat rabihim mushfiqun wajilwn mimaa khwwafhm allah taealaa bh
  23,58,"waldhyn hum ysddiqwn biayat allah fi alqran, wayaemalun bha"
  23,59,"waldhyn hum ykhlswn alebadt lilah whdh, wala yushrikun bih ghyrh"
  23,60,"waldhyn yjthdwn fi 'aemal alkhayr walbr, waqulubuhum khayft 'alaa tuqbl aemalhm, wa'alla tnjyhm min eadhab rabihim 'iidha rajaeuu 'iilayh llhsab"
  23,61,"awlyk almjthdwn fi altaet, dabhm almusaraeat 'iilaa kl eamal salh, wahum 'iilaa alkhayrat sabqwn"
  23,62,"wla nukalif ebdana min eibadina 'iilaa bima yseh aleamal bh, waemalhm mstwrt eindana fi kitab 'iihsa' al'aemal aldhy trfeh almalayikat yantiq bialhaqi elyhm, wala yuzlm ahd mnhm"
  23,63,"lkn qulub alkufaar fi dalal ghamr ean hdha alquran wama fyh, walahum mae shrkhm 'aemal syyt, yumhlhm allah lyemlwha, fynalu ghadib allah weqabh"
  23,64,"hta 'iidha 'akhadhna almtrfyn wa'ahl albtr minhum bedhabna, 'iidha hum yarfaeun 'aswatahum yatadaraeun mstghythyn"
  23,65,"fyqal lhm: la tsrkhu, wala tstghythu alyawm, 'iinakum la tastatieun nasr anfskm, wala yansurukum ahd min eadhab allh"
  23,66,"qd kanat ayat alquran tuqra elykm; lituminuu bha, fakuntum tnfrwn min smaeha waltsdyq bha, waleamal biha kama yafeal alnaks ealaa eaqibayh brjweh 'iilaa alwra'"
  23,67,"tfelwn dhlk mustakbirin ealaa alnaas bighayr alhaqi bsbb bayt allah alhram, tqwlwn: nahn 'ahlih la nughlab fyh, wttsamrwn hawlah balsyiy min alqwl"
  23,68,"aflm yatafakaruu fi alquran fyerfu sdqh, 'am manaeahum min al'iiman 'anah ja'ahum rasul wakitab lam yat aba'hm al'awalin mthlh, fankrwh waerdu enh?"
  23,69,"am manaeahum min aitibae alhaqu 'ana rasuluhum mhmdana salaa allah ealayh wasalam ghyr maeruf endhm, fahum munkarun lh?"
  23,70,"bl ahsbwh mjnwnana? laqad kdhabu; fa'iinama ja'ahum bialquran waltwhyd waldiyn alhq, wa'aktharuhum karihun lilhaqi hsdana wbghyana"
  23,71,"wlw sharae allah lahum maa ywafq 'ahwa'ahum lafasadat alsmwat wal'ard wman fyhn, bal 'ataynahum bma fyh ezhm wshrfhm, wahu alqran, fahum eanh merdwn"
  23,72,"bl 'amanehm min al'iiman 'anak - 'ayuha alrasul - tas'aluhum ajrana ealaa daewatak lahum fbkhlu? lam tafeal dhlk, fa'iina ma eind allah min althawab waleta' khyr, wahu khayr alrazqyn, fala yaqdr ahd 'ana yarzq mithl rizqah subhanah wteala"
  23,73,"w'ink - 'ayuha alrasul - ltdew qawmak wghyrhm 'iilaa dyn qwym, wahu din al'islam"
  23,74,"w'in aladhin la yusaddiqwn balbeth walhsab, wala yaemalun lhma, ean tariq aldiyn alqwym lmaylwn 'iilaa ghyrh"
  23,75,"wlw rahimnahum wakashafna eanhum ma bihim min qht wjwe latmadu fi alkufr walenad, ythyarwn wytkhbtwn"
  23,76,"walaqad abtlynahm bsnwf almsayb fama khdeu lrbhm, wama dewh khashiein eind nzwlha"
  23,77,"hta 'iidha fatahna ealayhim babana min aleadhab alshadid fi alakhrt, 'iidha hum fih ayswn min kuli khyr, mthyrwn la ydrwn ma ysnewn"